1. How to draw planisphere

~/python map.py

2. Files

map2.py ---------- Draw animation for 600,000 years. 
observe.py ------- Position of observation. 
stars.py --------- Draw stars with Hipparcos catalogue.
constlines.py ---- Draw constellation lines.
mathf.py --------- Basic functions to draw planisphere.
nameJ ------------ Most popular stars in Japanese.
constJ ----------- Constellation names in Japanese.
milkyway.py ------ Draw milkyway.
sky.py ----------- Draw background sky.
